   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><pb facs="Kerr_2487_001_01"/>Dr. Paul Goldmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168">Berlin W<unclear>.</unclear></rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb40583">Dessauerstraße 19</rs>.</hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><seg><seg rend="left"><pb facs="Kerr_2487_001_02"/><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="bold">Gruss</hi> aus <rs type="place" ref="#pmb46000">Grundlsee</rs>.</hi></seg><seg rend="right"><hi rend="pre-print">Totalansicht.</hi></seg></seg></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="Kerr_2487_001_02"/>Ich bin hier per Rad, <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03188-1"/>aus <rs type="place" ref="#pmb34401"><hi rend="latintype">Altaussee</hi></rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03188-1"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler</rs> hielt sich seit <ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1900-06-29" subtype="date-only"/> in <rs type="place" ref="#pmb34401">Altaussee</rs> auf. Am <ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1900-07-03" subtype="date-only"/> fuhr er
                  weiter nach <rs type="place" ref="#pmb49312">Admont</rs>.</note>, (<rs type="person" ref="#pmb10863">Richard</rs> nicht.) – Die berühmte <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03188-2"/>Fußpartie<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03188-2"><ref type="schnitzler-briefe" target="L02920" subtype="See"/>.
               </note> wäre am erwün<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chte<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ten we<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ie etwa <date when="1900-08-15">Mitte Augu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t</date> begänne. Rendezvous <rs type="place" ref="#pmb30">Salzburg</rs> oder <rs type="place" ref="#pmb867">Innsbruck</rs>. – Nach <rs type="place" ref="#pmb30">Salzburg</rs> auf ein paar
               Tage könnte <rs type="person" ref="#pmb10863">Richard</rs> (u ich) (und <rs type="person" ref="#pmb26392">Leo</rs>) auch <date when="1900-08-01">Anfang
                  Augu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t</date>.</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t <signed>Arthur</signed></closer><postscript><p>Bitte das auch <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03188-3"/><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb11910">Kerr</rs></hi> zu<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>agen<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03188-3"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb11485">Goldmann</rs> sandte die Karte direkt weiter,
                     sie ist im Nachlass <rs type="person" ref="#pmb11910">Kerrs</rs>
                     überliefert.</note></p></postscript></div>
      </body>
